keyFacts: An FBI email address (dropbox@icibi.gov) sent an email on August 26, 2019, regarding Jeffrey Epstein.
The email contained an attached document titled 'Epstein_conf call_summary_08-26-2019.docx'.
The document appears to be a summary of a conference call about Epstein, uploaded via FBI networks (FBINET to UNET).
The email's date (August 26, 2019) is shortly after Jeffrey Epstein's death in custody on August 10, 2019.
The correspondence suggests ongoing FBI activity or communication regarding the Epstein case in late August 2019.
